column5: Epsin-1 is a ubiquitously expressed endocytic adaptor protein that is involved in clathrin-mediated endocytosis.
IFI6 is a gene that encodes a protein that is involved in the regulation of interferon-mediated antiviral responses.
ISG15 is a ubiquitin-like protein that is induced by interferon and is involved in antiviral and anti-tumor responses.
